Endpoint and method Authentication Parameter(s) Description Example /host/registering<code>POST</code> <code>&lt;APIKEY&gt;</code> <code>hostname</code> (required)<code>ip</code> (required) Register a host to Repomanager and retrieve host ID and token <pre><code>curl --fail-with-body --post301 -L -s -X POST -H "Authorization: Bearer &lt;APIKEY&gt;" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"hostname":"&lt;FQDN&gt;","ip":"&lt;IP&gt;"}' https://repomanager.mydomain.net/api/v2/host/registering
</code></pre> /host/registering<code>DELETE</code> <code>&lt;HOST_ID&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;</code> Unregister a host from Repomanager <pre><code>curl --fail-with-body --post301 -L -s -X DELETE -H "Authorization: Host &lt;HOST_ID&gt;:&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;" -H "Content-Type: application/json" https://repomanager.mydomain.net/api/v2/host/registering
</code></pre> /host/status<code>PUT</code> <code>&lt;HOST_ID&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;</code> <code>hostname</code> (optional)<code>os</code> (optional)<code>os_version</code> (optional)<code>os_family</code> (optional)<code>type</code> (=virtualization type) (optional)<code>kernel</code> (optional)<code>arch</code> (optional)<code>profile</code> (optional)<code>env</code> (optional)<code>agent_status</code> (optional)<code>linupdate_version</code> (optional)<code>reboot_required</code> (optional) Send host general information to Repomanager <pre><code>curl --fail-with-body --post301 -L -s -X PUT -H "Authorization: Host &lt;HOST_ID&gt;:&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"hostname":"myfqdn.localhost","os":"ubuntu","os_version":"22.04","os_family":"Debian","type":"Bare metal","kernel":"5.15.0-89-generic","arch":"x86_64","profile":"PC","env":"prod","agent_status":"running","linupdate_version":"2.2.2","reboot_required":"false"}' https://repomanager.mydomain.net/api/v2/host/status
</code></pre> /host/packages/installed<code>PUT</code> <code>&lt;HOST_ID&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;</code> <code>installed_packages</code> (required)Each package must be separated by a comma and contains the package name and the version number separated by a pipe Send list of installed packages to Repomanager <pre><code>curl --fail-with-body --post301 -L -s -X PUT -H "Authorization: Host &lt;HOST_ID&gt;:&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"installed_packages":"accountsservice|22.07.5-2ubuntu1.4,acl|2.3.1-1,acpi-support|0.144,acpid|1:2.0.33-1ubuntu1,add-apt-key|1.0-0.5,adduser, etc..."}' https://repomanager.mydomain.net/api/v2/host/packages/installed
</code></pre> /host/packages/available<code>PUT</code> <code>&lt;HOST_ID&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;</code> <code>available_packages</code> (required)Each package must be separated by a comma and contains the package name and the version number separated by a pipe Send list of available packages (can be updated) to Repomanager <pre><code>curl --fail-with-body --post301 -L -s -X PUT -H "Authorization: Host &lt;HOST_ID&gt;:&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"available_packages":"accountsservice|22.07.6-2ubuntu1,add-apt-key|1.0-0.6,adduser|3.118ubuntu5, etc..."}' https://repomanager.mydomain.net/api/v2/host/packages/available
</code></pre> /host/packages/event<code>PUT</code> <code>&lt;HOST_ID&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;</code> <code>events</code> (required) Send package event history (installed / upgraded / removed / downgraded) to Repomanager <pre><code>curl --fail-with-body --post301 -L -s -X PUT -H "Authorization: Host &lt;HOST_ID&gt;:&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '
{
    "events": [
        {
            "date_start": "2022-11-01",
            "date_end": "2022-11-01",
            "time_start": "12:47:30",
            "time_end": "12:47:57",
            "command": "/usr/bin/apt upgrade",
            "upgraded": [
                {
                    "name": "firefox-locale-en",
                    "version": "106.0.3+linuxmint1+vanessa"
                },
                {
                    "name": "php8.1-opcache",
                    "version": "8.1.12-1+ubuntu22.04.1+deb.sury.org+1"
                },
            ],
        },
        {
            "date_start": "2022-11-05",
            "date_end": "2022-11-05",
            "time_start": "12:21:40",
            "time_end": "12:21:41",
            "command": "/usr/bin/apt install php8.1-curl",
            "installed": [
                {
                    "name": "php8.1-curl",
                    "version": "8.1.12-1+ubuntu22.04.1+deb.sury.org+1"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "date_start": "2022-11-16",
            "date_end": "2022-11-16",
            "time_start": "16:26:15",
            "time_end": "16:26:20",
            "command": "/usr/bin/apt autoremove",
            "removed": [
                {
                    "name": "linux-headers-5.15.0-50-generic",
                    "version": "5.15.0-50.56"
                },
                {
                    "name": "linux-modules-5.15.0-50-generic",
                    "version": "5.15.0-50.56"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}' https://repomanager.mydomain.net/api/v2/host/packages/event
</code></pre> /profile<code>GET</code> <code>&lt;APIKEY&gt;</code>or<code>&lt;HOST_ID&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;</code> Retrieve all available profile configurations <pre><code>curl --fail-with-body -L -s -X GET -H "Authorization: Host &lt;HOST_ID&gt;:&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;" https://repomanager.mydomain.net/api/v2/profile | jq
</code></pre> /profile/<code>&lt;PROFILE&gt;</code><code>GET</code> <code>&lt;APIKEY&gt;</code>or<code>&lt;HOST_ID&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;</code> Retrieve profile's global configuration <pre><code>curl --fail-with-body -L -s -X GET -H "Authorization: Host &lt;HOST_ID&gt;:&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;" https://repomanager.mydomain.net/api/v2/profile/app_server | jq
</code></pre> /profile/<code>&lt;PROFILE&gt;</code>/excludes<code>GET</code> <code>&lt;APIKEY&gt;</code>or<code>&lt;HOST_ID&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;</code> Retrieve profile's package exclusion configuration <pre><code>curl --fail-with-body -L -s -X GET -H "Authorization: Host &lt;HOST_ID&gt;:&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;" https://repomanager.mydomain.net/api/v2/profile/app_server/excludes | jq
</code></pre> /profile/<code>&lt;PROFILE&gt;</code>/repos<code>GET</code> <code>&lt;APIKEY&gt;</code>or<code>&lt;HOST_ID&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;</code> Retrieve profile's repository configuration <pre><code>curl --fail-with-body -L -s -X GET -H "Authorization: Host &lt;HOST_ID&gt;:&lt;HOST_TOKEN&gt;" https://repomanager.mydomain.net/api/v2/profile/app_server/repos | jq
</code></pre>
